title: Ensemble La Fenice
text:
Ensemble La Fenice is a period wind band based in the town of Auxerre in the Burgundy region of France. 
Founded in 1990 by the cornett player Jean Tub√©ry, the ensemble specializes in music of the Baroque era played on period instruments.
